cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it focuses on object recognition and grasping in robotic systems. It also utilizes support vector machines (SVM) for classification, which is a common technique in robotics. Computer Vision (cs.CV) is also a likely sub-category as the paper deals with 3D object recognition and classification. Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) are also possible sub-categories as the paper proposes a new feature descriptor for object recognition and classification. Finally, Graphics (cs.GR) is a possible sub-category as the paper deals with 3D object surfaces and textures.
